                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6743" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0463</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8409 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共识共创、共享共赢：易天股份积分制绩效管理变革探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Consensus and Creation, Sharing and Win-win: Etmade’ the Exploration Road of Point-based Performance Management Change</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄丽，聂婧，赵开元</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市易天自动化设备股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绩效管理；积分制；积分制绩效管理；员工激励；新生代员工</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Performance management; point system; point-based performance management; employee motivation; new generation employees</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易天股份是一家专业从事电子专用设备、集研、产、销为一体的高新技术企业，是国内为数不多同时兼具全自动平板显示模组组装设备研发和生产能力的企业。随着业务拓展、人员增加，延用的KPI绩效管理暴露出考评维度不够全面、无法有效识别和激励关键人才等一系列弊端。为此，公司决定探索一种既可以保留传统KPI的已有优势，又能从多维度对员工进行客观公正评价的积分易天股份是一家专业从事电子专用设备、集研、产、销为一体的高新技术企业，是国内为数不多同时兼具全自动平板显示模组组装设备研发和生产能力的企业。随着业务拓展、人员增加，延用的KPI绩效考核暴露出维度不够全面、无法有效识别和激励关键人才等一系列弊端。为此，公司决定探索一种既可以保留传统KPI的已有优势，又能从多维度对员工进行客观公正评价的积分制绩效管理方法。本案例以易天股份简介——原KPI问题凸显——积分制绩效管理初步方案出台受阻——“第一版方案”毁誉参半——“第二版方案”框架构建——“第二版方案”试点成功——尾声为故事逻辑主线，通过对易天股份绩效管理变革的动因、过程、内容和结果的分析，旨在启发案例使用者应用积分制管理、绩效管理、激励理论等对案例问题进行思考，理解积分制绩效管理的设计要点、管理流程以及如何促成对员工的有效激励等。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstract: Etmade is a high-tech enterprise specializing in electronic special equipment, integrating research, production and sales. It is one of the few enterprises in China that has both R&amp;D and production capacity of automatic flat panel display module assembly equipment. With the expansion of business and the increase of staff, the KPI performance management has revealed a series of drawbacks, such as the evaluation dimension is not comprehensive enough and cannot effectively identify and motivate key talents. Therefore, the company decided to explore a point-based performance management method that could retain the existing advantages of traditional KPI, but also provide objective and fair evaluation of employees from multiple dimensions. This case is based on the logical line of the story: Introduction of Etmade Industry——the problems of the original KPI performance management are highlighted-the initial scheme of point-based performance management is blocked——the “first version of the scheme” has mixed reputation——Framework construction of “the second version scheme”——the “second version of the scheme” is successful in the pilot——the end, through the introduction of Etmade Industry Through the analysis of the motivation, process, content and results of the performance management change, the aim is to inspire the case users to apply the point system management, performance management and motivation theory to think about the case problems and understand the design points of the point system performance management, the management process and how to promote the effective motivation of employees.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《绩效管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绩效管理的概念、流程以及与绩效考核的区别；积分制绩效管理概念及其优点；锦标赛理论；公平理论；自我决定理论；绩效管理的目的；积分制绩效管理设计要点</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
